name: in real life coin
description: The popular phrase "IRL" meaning "in real life", has been increasingly viral. There is a new trend of people drawing their coins and charts on paper, and saying they're trading "IRL". We tokenized one of these viral drawings, and have formed a community that is encouraging young crypto traders to get outside and do things in real life, while also allowing them to hold the social stock of the popular phrase "IRL".
